ykłym przypadkiem medycznym. John zostaje przewieziony do londyńskiego szpitala i z pomocą lekarza odzyskuje wiarę w siebie oraz godność utracone przed laty w objazdowym cyrku. Z czasem okazało się, że John to inteligentna i wrażliwa osoba, która staje się ozdobą wiktoriańskich salonów.","popularity":4.742,"poster_path":"/qxjlkIADVx8MvtzNXVCtrrYocAV.jpg","release_date":"1980-10-09","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":8.049,"vote_count":3934,"character":"Man in the Bowler Hat in the Mob Chasing Merrick (uncredited)","credit_id":"563d583b9251417819005e63","order":63},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/4KeE9os5PVbaEg02OJ4Vt1aXDXQ.jpg","genre_ids":[35],"id":359115,"title":"Out Yonder — Neighbor Boy","original_language":"en","original_title":"Out Yonder — Neighbor Boy","overview":"","popularity":0.2651,"poster_path":"/oV23w4rcYQxRHDHppTs2OJk1hjS.jpg","release_date":"2002-02-11","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":6.2,"vote_count":15,"character":"","credit_id":"56b0066f9251410b460005b2","order":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/ijcV9hwbgCnAZFHlLD68buipUG1.jpg","genre_ids":[99,10402],"id":413812,"title":"This Is Sparklehorse","original_language":"en","original_title":"This Is Sparklehorse","overview":"","popularity":0.1672,"poster_path":"/bCx5KMcHu5H1GMeQX60CpVfkw48.jpg","release_date":"2022-10-12","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":0.0,"vote_count":0,"character":"Self","credit_id":"6658fe5c97b7c5247574f116","order":4},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/pmmPUfLIGa80TFJd8bDSz9SDGzY.jpg","genre_ids":[99],"id":219292,"title":"What Is Cinema?","original_language":"en","original_title":"What Is Cinema?","overview":"","popularity":0.4433,"poster_path":"/a7lscT93aGgvD6W5Po7dTVLdv19.jpg","release_date":"2013-09-06","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":6.5,"vote_count":24,"character":"Self","credit_id":"57338fbe92514140b40006b5","order":2},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"genre_ids":[99],"id":706599,"title":"Jonathan Ross Presents for One Week Only: David Lynch","original_language":"en","original_title":"Jonathan Ross Presents for One Week Only: David Lynch","overview":"","popularity":0.7227,"poster_path":"/kX8ZqvvCba3ZlTKgZGxSjCrEovR.jpg","release_date":"1990-10-19","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.5,"vote_count":2,"character":"Self","credit_id":"666bd38edcec41d278b975f9","order":1},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/qJGioJgsqpoDUiAztWcxCB3vn2b.jpg","genre_ids":[99],"id":381071,"title":"My Beautiful Broken Brain","original_language":"en","original_title":"My Beautiful Broken Brain","overview":"Codzienne zmagania, porażki i sukcesy kobiety, która w wieku 34 lat doznała udaru mózgu i na nowo uczy się mówić, czytać i pisać.","popularity":0.397,"poster_path":"/onm7B851Jk90Krcw9cfBdkTRhyg.jpg","release_date":"2014-11-21","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.1,"vote_count":67,"character":"Self","credit_id":"5780fea19251417928002f5e","order":4},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"genre_ids":[99,27,14,53,18,35],"id":936972,"title":"Dynamic:01: The Best of DavidLynch.com","original_language":"en","original_title":"Dynamic:01: The Best of DavidLynch.com","overview":"","popularity":0.3164,"poster_path":"/bUTVSQuXGnOV1d6p0eZWZ7Nwn9y.jpg","release_date":"2007-01-30","softcore":false,"video":true,"vote_average":5.5,"vote_count":2,"character":"himself","credit_id":"667c389a86619eb1b0759874","order":3},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/josJUt5eVMANf06mxSKnJlwjELB.jpg","genre_ids":[18],"id":407449,"title":"Szczęściarz","original_language":"en","original_title":"Lucky","overview":"Lucky jest szczęściarzem. Dobiega powoli 90-tki, ale jego serce, krążenie i układ odpornościowy są w naprawdę niezłym stanie. Nawet płuca, mimo że od lat pali tyle, że zabiłoby to znacznie młodszego mężczyznę. Życie Lucky’ego jest wybijane rytmem codziennej rutyny, od porannej gimnastyki po obchód po znajomych sklepach, kafejkach i barach. Znajduje tam za każdym razem przyjaciół i znajomych, z którymi może porozmawiać, podroczyć się, porozwiązywać krzyżówki. Pewnego dnia upada we własnym domu. Przypadkiem. Nie wiadomo dlaczego. Lekarza stać jedynie na dość banalną diagnozę – choroba nazywa się starość – ale Lucky zostaje wyrwany ze swej monotonnej rutyny. Zaczyna angażować się emocjonalnie w dyskusje z przyjaciółmi. Traktuje inaczej ludzi, którzy mu się narazili. Otwiera się, prawdopodobnie pierwszy raz od wielu lat, na nieznajomych. Uświadamia sobie, że jego rola na tym świecie dobiega powoli końca i jedyne, co może zrobić, to ten fakt zaakceptować. I się uśmiechnąć.","popularity":1.2874,"poster_path":"/fy2K8jqCV9rNC8fHx9muPJTNaqs.jpg","release_date":"2017-09-29","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.302,"vote_count":642,"character":"Howard","credit_id":"5790cd3c9251416b4500179e","order":1},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/9qMP1aquRST8XfJ58EqTMAZ9kA6.jpg","genre_ids":[99],"id":413765,"title":"David Lynch: The Art Life","original_language":"en","original_title":"David Lynch: The Art Life","overview":"","popularity":0.6901,"poster_path":"/pgtQceTZKylB2B237t18h2pOXpE.jpg","release_date":"2017-02-15","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":6.966,"vote_count":218,"character":"Self","credit_id":"57e05349c3a3684dd7007ded","order":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/jFI3RfIoXT3gaRu20j8Ej6H6Mrg.jpg","genre_ids":[99],"id":413784,"title":"Blue Velvet Revisited","original_language":"en","original_title":"Blue Velvet Revisited","overview":"","popularity":0.6063,"poster_path":"/xTazJzE53wi5OZ0jwzoG9ButkzE.jpg","release_date":"2016-10-07","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":6.909,"vote_count":11,"character":"Self","credit_id":"580f60a8c3a3687ac400ad9e","order":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/zmv4dhhX5IugcyJl777xTMmkQgn.jpg","genre_ids":[99],"id":425057,"title":"Shadows of Paradise","original_language":"en","original_title":"Shadows of Paradise","overview":"","popularity":0.093,"poster_path":"/yxGb8T4EYBEt203mYkQVRXjn4Cm.jpg","release_date":"2016-10-11","softcore"